{"parse":{"title":"While Mortals Sleep (short story collection)","pageid":30007258,"revid":840492955,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption style=\"font-style:italic;padding-bottom:0.2em;\">While Mortals Sleep <span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=While+Mortals+Sleep&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BKurt+Vonnegut%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2011+in+literature%7C2011%5D%5D&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BDelacorte+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft.pages=272\"></span></caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:WhileMortalsSleep.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"WhileMortalsSleep.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b4/WhileMortalsSleep.jpg/220px-WhileMortalsSleep.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b4/WhileMortalsSleep.jpg 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"240\" data-file-height=\"363\" /></a><div>First edition</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Kurt_Vonnegut\" title=\"Kurt Vonnegut\">Kurt Vonnegut</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Cover&#160;artist</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Kurt_Vonnegut\" title=\"Kurt Vonnegut\">Kurt Vonnegut</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\nUnited States</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Delacorte_Press\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Delacorte Press\">Delacorte Press</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Publication date</div></th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/2011_in_literature\" title=\"2011 in literature\">2011</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Pages</th><td>\n272</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a></th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-385-34373-2\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-385-34373-2\">978-0-385-34373-2</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Preceded&#160;by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/wiki/Look_at_the_Birdie\" title=\"Look at the Birdie\">Look at the Birdie</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>While Mortals Sleep</b></i> is a collection of sixteen previously unpublished short stories by <a href=\"/wiki/Kurt_Vonnegut\" title=\"Kurt Vonnegut\">Kurt Vonnegut</a>, released on January 25, 2011. It is the third posthumously published Kurt Vonnegut book, the first being <i><a href=\"/wiki/Armageddon_in_Retrospect\" title=\"Armageddon in Retrospect\">Armageddon in Retrospect</a></i>, the second being <i><a href=\"/wiki/Look_at_the_Birdie\" title=\"Look at the Birdie\">Look at the Birdie</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The book begins with a foreword by <a href=\"/wiki/Dave_Eggers\" title=\"Dave Eggers\">Dave Eggers</a>. Illustrations by Vonnegut himself appear throughout.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Contents\">Contents</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=While_Mortals_Sleep_(short_story_collection)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Contents\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ol><li>\"Jenny\"</li>\n<li>\"The Epizootic\"</li>\n<li>\"Hundred-Dollar Kisses\"</li>\n<li>\"Guardian of the Person\"</li>\n<li>\u201cWith His Hand on the Throttle\"</li>\n<li>\"Girl Pool\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cRuth\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cWhile Mortals Sleep\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cOut, Brief Candle\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cTango\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cBomar\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cThe Man Without No Kiddleys\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201cMr. Z\u201d</li>\n<li>\u201c$10,000 a Year, Easy\u201d</li>\n<li>\"Money Talks\u201d</li>\n<li>\"The Humbugs\"</li></ol>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=While_Mortals_Sleep_(short_story_collection)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Sheehan, William (February 15, 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/02/14/AR2011021406069.html\">\"Book review: 'While Mortals Sleep' by Kurt Vonnegut\"</a>. Washington Post<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">18 February</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Book+review%3A+%27While+Mortals+Sleep%27+by+Kurt+Vonnegut&amp;rft.date=2011-02-15&amp;rft.aulast=Sheehan&amp;rft.aufirst=William&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwp-dyn%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2F2011%2F02%2F14%2FAR2011021406069.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWhile+Mortals+Sleep+%28short+story+collection%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Hopley, Claire (April 1, 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2011/apr/1/book-review-while-mortals-sleep/\">\"BOOK REVIEW: 'While Mortals Sleep<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. The Washing